data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, owned by a military family, is set to deploy in March, prompting all offers to be considered. Situated in the heart of Lynn Haven within a predominantly military-owned neighborhood, this residence embodies comfort and style. Boasting a convenient location, the property features an open concept layout, making it an ideal space for both day-to-day living and entertaining.Upon entering, the home is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Modern elegance is enhanced by sleek vinyl plank flooring, setting the tone for the entire home. To the left, a generously sized living room awaits, providing ample space for gatherings with friends and family. Further exploration reveals spacious interiors with soaring ceilings, an open kitchen featuring a breakfast bar, and a dining room seamlessly connected to the backyard oasis through a sliding glass door.The backyard is adorned with a sizable pool, inviting lazy summer days and outdoor entertaining. It serves as the perfect retreat for relaxation and enjoyment. Moving down the hallway, three separate bedrooms and a well-appointed guest bathroom await. The two bedrooms on the right are ideal for kids or guests, conveniently sharing the hallway bathroom. The master bedroom, situated at the end of the hallway, offers tranquility with fantastic natural lighting, a beautifully designed shower, and double vanity sinks.Lynn Haven, a highly sought-after location in the Panhandle, provides a plethora of amenities, including world-class dining, parks, and shopping. Seize the opportunity to make this home yours and relish in the best that the community has to offer. Don't miss out on the chance to own a piece of Lynn Haven paradise! Call now to schedule your private showing and experience the charm of this exceptional property firsthand. Your dream home awaits!
